---

## Project structure

```
vsss_sim/
├── __init__.py     gymnasium registration, package exports
├── config.py       IEEE VSS constants (field, robot, ball)
├── physics.py      2-D physics engine (diff-drive, collisions)
├── env.py          VSSEnv – Gymnasium Env subclass
└── rendering.py    Pygame renderer (human / rgb_array)
tests/
├── test_config.py  spec-compliance checks
├── test_physics.py kinematics & collision unit tests
└── test_env.py     Gymnasium interface tests
pyproject.toml
requirements.txt
```

